  m_text: 'Here I am, in the hell out there. I have maintained my reputation as Fearless
    detective Amarjot Singh in my whole life. But now, it seems like I am done. A
    terrorist has challenged me to find a bomb in the city.  Are you serious!. And
    I have to do it alone. Never mind, I will do it.........


    Let''s look at
    the clue given to me....


    The cameras record things that human eye sometime
    misses. The dawn is the limit. Countdown has started.........'
