  continueHint: {fileID: 81686319}
  introAudio: {fileID: 548683998}
  fullIntroText: 'Here I am, in the hell out there. I have maintained my reputation
    as Fearless detective Amarjot Singh in my whole life. But now, it seems like
    I am done. A terrorist has challenged me to find a bomb in the city.  Are you
    serious!. And I have to do it alone. Never mind, I will do it.........


    Let''s
    look at the clue given to me....


    The cameras records things that human
    eye sometime misses.....'
  typingSpeed: 0.04
  fadeDuration: 1.5
  audioFadeDuration: 1.5
